Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,行け！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,くっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,ファイトー！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.49,0:22:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,頑張れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,あと少し！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:22:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,んぐっ
